These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, ivory, purple
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, satire, spy
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, daffodil
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, polish
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, train, trike
 1. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 2. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 3. the person who likes purple is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 4. the person watching crime movies is the polish##1
 5. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the german##3
 7. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 9. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
10. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
11. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the lawyer##8
13. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person who likes lavender##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Color          | lavender | ivory | purple    |
| Job           | fisherman | lawyer   | nurse     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | satire   | spy       |
| Flower   | dahlia    | daffodil   | lily     |
| Nationality   | polish    | german   | pakistani |
| Transport     | trike     | airplane | train     |

