House: cape-cod, art-deco, tower
 1. the person eating pear is the prince-smoker##1
 2. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the tower house##1
 4. the art-deco house is not to the right of the russian##8
 5. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 6. the italian is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 7. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the russian##8
 8. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
 9. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the russian##3
10. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the left of the accountant##1
12. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
13. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
14. the accountant is the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3        |
