 4. the thai is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is not the person driving the trike##6
 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
 7. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the thai##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is not the person driving the trike##6
10. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
11. the person eating kiwi is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
12. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1

