.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, trike
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, paramedic, videographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, drama, fantasy
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, thai
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, may
 1. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 5. the person driving the bus is not the person watching crime movies##6
 6. the thai is the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
10. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8

